				<img class="hvres-variant-img lazy" data-original="/pic/kt/-Cp4DswufgcvFtHvtryMCQ.gif" /></span></div><p class="hvres-source">Dị thể</p>		<div class="hvres-meaning"><a href="/whv/啼"><span class="hvres-variant han">&#21884;</span></a><a href="/whv/諟"><span class="hvres-variant han">&#35551;</span></a><a href="/whv/谛"><span class="hvres-variant han">&#35867;</span></a><a href="/whv/𧫚"><span class="hvres-variant han">&#162522;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>		<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Quang/Du-Tr%E1%BA%A5n-B%E1%BA%AFc-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-wBWEwSdLbCE1uUS6O6VmJQ">Du Trấn Bắc tự - 遊鎮北寺</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/V%C5%A9-Quang/author-w-SBZQPTSV_LzY0StAT7Dw">Vũ Quang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/D%E1%BB%AF-thi-h%E1%BB%AFu-Phan-Long-Tr%C3%A2n-du-C%C3%B4n-S%C6%A1n-nh%C3%A2n-t%C3%A1c-C%C3%B4n-S%C6%A1n-h%C3%A0nh-v%C3%A2n/poem-c66Lkci6txOArDMiGj9TPw">Dữ thi hữu Phan Long Trân du Côn Sơn nhân tác Côn Sơn hành vân - 與詩友潘龍珍遊崑山因作崑山行云</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-l%E1%BB%AF-ho%C3%A0i-ng%C3%A2m/poem-QwHBlDHxHjNmmwiMhPsXpg">Thu dạ lữ hoài ngâm - 秋夜旅懷吟</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/%C4%90inh-Nh%E1%BA%ADt-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-Hrw_uUvQJ05Gjc8O2RkROQ">Đinh Nhật Thận</a>)<br/></div>		</div>
